scenes.description: Cecilia reacts in distress to her burning overturned car and then saves it with a water gun.
Cecilia introduces her 3D debut merch: the Otomo Pouch and Socks.
Cecilia showcases her 1st Anniversary Merch Set.
Cecilia prepares the audience for a song and teases a huge announcement following the performance.
Transition to the performance stage with crowd cheering and Cecilia thanking everyone.
